@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container py-5" style="max-width:900px;">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4 text-center"> About Outdoorways</h1>

    <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <img src="~/logo.png" height="60" alt="Alternate Text" />
    </div>

    <p class="lead" style="color:#555;">
        At <strong>Outdoorways</strong>, we believe that every adventure begins with the right gear.
        Whether you're heading out for a mountain hike, exploring new trails, or simply enjoying the outdoors
        close to home, we provide durable, comfortable, and stylish apparel made to keep up with your journey.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4" style="color:#555;">
        Our mission is simple: <strong>to make the outdoors accessible to everyone</strong>.
        From lightweight essentials to warm winter layers, our products blend performance, comfort,
        and design to help you stay ready for wherever the path leads.
        We carefully select high-quality materials and timeless styles that last season after season.
    </p>

    <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-5">What We Stand For</h3>
    <ul class="mt-3" style="color:#555; line-height:1.8;">
        <li><strong>Quality First:</strong> Durable fabrics, functional designs, and reliable craftsmanship.</li>
        <li><strong>Comfort & Performance:</strong> Gear designed to keep you warm, dry, and protected.</li>
        <li><strong>Adventure for All:</strong> Apparel suitable for every experience level — from beginner to expert.</li>
        <li><strong>Sustainable Thinking:</strong> We prioritize long-lasting products to reduce waste and encourage mindful consumption.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="fw-semibold mt-5">Our Story</h3>
    <p class="mt-3" style="color:#555;">
        Born from the passion of explorers who understand the value of reliable outdoor gear,
        Outdoorways started with one goal: <strong>to create a brand people can trust</strong>.
        What began as a small idea has grown into a collection built for adventurers worldwide —
        individuals who appreciate authenticity, simplicity, and the beauty of nature.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-3" style="color:#555;">
        Today, we continue to expand our catalog and improve our designs, driven by your feedback and
        the evolving needs of the outdoor community. Whether you're climbing peaks, camping under the stars,
        or simply taking a walk on a chilly day — <strong>we’re here to support your journey</strong>.
    </p>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4" href="/Home/Index">Explore Our Products</a>
    </div>
</div>
